Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:04.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽は雄  男性を表し…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:05.15,Default,Ed,0,0,0,,The sun is male, and represents a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:08.23,Default,Al,0,0,0,,And the moon is female; representing a woman.
